  "commentary": "With SPX at 6759.16 sitting right between the massive negative gamma wall at 6750 (-8673M) and positive gamma at 6780 (+6909M), dealers are caught in a high-volatility pocket where small moves get amplified. The recent GEX surge combined with spot trading above the 6720 flip but below max positive gamma means dealers will aggressively sell any push toward 6780 while providing strong support if we drift back toward the 6750 cluster of negative strikes. Watch 6750 as the critical support level where dealer buying should kick in hard, and 6780 as the resistance where dealer selling intensifies.\n\nBottom line: expect volatile but range-bound action between 6750-6780 with strong reactions at both levels.",
